      },
      "content": "I think the story that was shared in the Mythos System Card still has the signs of flawed LLM writing (which looks like good writing at a glance): A story that doesn't really hold together logically, but sounds like it should. The back-and-forth banter. Lack of characters.\n\nWriting fiction is hard!",
